{
  "id": 18,
  "title": "#18 Entering money land",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Hey,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Short one today - today I'm exhausted, it's 11pm and we just had another big day riding :)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Here we go 🎉🥳"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/9ab9dc74-2fd3-49cf-b5fb-cd1777c50bc1/IMG_7585.jpeg",
      "caption": "going down the coast in Moni"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "June 6th"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We arrived at Mani (Μανης) mi, omicron, ni, eita, sigma (now I know all my Greek letters math class is gonna be a breezeee)"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/49ddb771-9b58-4acd-8236-9272941ec115/IMG_7403.jpeg",
      "caption": "Welcome to mani (ΜAΝΗΣ)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We finally arrived at the top of the mani peninsula. We heard so much about it and we were excited to check it out."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/006e9989-e582-4706-b33e-788a482f0094/IMG_7406.jpeg",
      "caption": "Entering gythio"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We first entered Gythio - an awesome waterfront town."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/c9535b35-29d9-48b2-9fdc-7d2738d3ab53/IMG_7412.jpeg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We found a beach about 25 km into the ride and took naps in the midday sun. It's really starting to be terrible biking between 11am-3pm."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/8ac5bc0a-5eff-4cb8-9550-ef0de7e68cb6/IMG_7444.jpeg",
      "caption": "View from roads around Moni"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Mani has incredible views from the roads along the coast."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/bb555cf9-a1c0-478b-bd75-d0c8bb7e067f/IMG_7460.jpeg",
      "caption": "We stopped at a cafe and I ate this delicious Greek salad"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/a578e283-430f-4a72-b58a-27e383786bdc/IMG_7469.jpeg",
      "caption": "Campspot"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When it got dark we found a private beach with an incredible view of the the ocean - our day ended sleeping a few feet from the water."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/5f54b570-d816-4a1c-bcef-f5554eeb45b3/IMG_7471.jpeg",
      "caption": "I used the tent for mosquitoes."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Until tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Erik"
    }
  ]
}